><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Fract.\">Fract.</a></title_> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">28</biblScope></bibl>, cf. <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0627.tlg012.perseus-grc1:1:22\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <title_ TEIform=\"title\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Aph.\">Aph.</a></title_> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">1.22</biblScope></bibl>. </sense> <sense n=\"II\" id=\"n74764.2\" level=\"2\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"sense\"> of men, <xr opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"xr\"> <lbl opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"lbl\">like</lbl> <ref targOrder=\"U\" lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"ref\">σφριγάω</ref></xr>, <tr_ opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tr\">swell</tr_> with lust, <tr_ opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tr\">wax wanton, be rampant,</tr_> <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0019.tlg007.perseus-grc1:1113\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Ar.\">Ar.</a></author> <title_ TEIform=\"title\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Lys.\">Lys.</a></title_> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">1113</biblScope></bibl>, <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0019.tlg006.perseus-grc1:462\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <title_ TEIform=\"title\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Av.\">Av.</a></title_> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">462</biblScope> </bibl> (where the Sch. explains it <foreign lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"foreign\">ἐπιθυμητικῶς ἔχω</foreign>) ; <cit TEIform=\"cit\"> <quote_ lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"quote\">ὁ ἐπ᾽ ἀφροδισίοις μαινόμενος . . ὀργῶν</quote_> <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0542.tlg001:6:188\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\">Poll.</author> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">6.188</biblScope> </bibl> </cit> ; of human beings and animals, <tr_ opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tr\">to be in heat, desire sexual intercourse,</tr_> <foreign lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"foreign\">ὀργᾶν πρὸς τὴν ὁμιλίαν, ὀχείαν,</foreign> <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0086.tlg014:542a:32\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Arist.\">Arist.</a></autho